Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用自責
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終究是個人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾 逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來猜中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.83,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}捕食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角得知戀人死去的場面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領導者不在的話豈不是很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些我不去的話就無法解決的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也能久違的好好享受享受學校生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 我很乖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cut cut
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近總覺得集有些不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是無所顧忌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得像另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許在大島發生了什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南方島嶼的休假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛夏的戀愛冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後從少年踏上了成人的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的 人生總是事與願違呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說谷尋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去過設施了 但是說他沒來過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明以前曾一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 尋找的東西在水族館裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是在找魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？戀愛的幸運物品是虎紋的茶壺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？那種東西要到哪裡去找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎紋的茶壺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你們倆都還沒回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 櫻滿同學的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颯太攝影用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人的遺物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正說是給祈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我有東西落在活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我拿去給他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你代替我陪祭逛街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 花音醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運的機會哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油 幸運機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運機會是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…什麼來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有幽靈出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:05:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人用櫻滿庫洛斯的ID進入了大島研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼要解釋的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛斯博士曾經的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莖道修一郎博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡下車 購物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多東西買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能拿得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷尋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 要去快活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的谷尋同學 這只是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷尋 你沒有其他話要說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我在這把一切和盤托出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭 拜託你一個人去購物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要和谷尋說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻滿集 我一直盯著你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是正確的選擇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙 說要處分潤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們趁著騷動逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不能再把潤放在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是出賣了你才換來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還是逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又掉下來了嗎 有哪裡疼嗎 潤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 潤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經捕捉到逃亡中的結晶化患者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.19,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(794,665)}cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 好傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個結晶化患者有必要出動我的人形兵器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:20.51,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(695,665)}cancer                                   endrave
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 boy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍在打倒史萊姆的時候也是使出全力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍會吃史萊姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 傷疤臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 丹 這之後就交給我吧 全力完成任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是處世技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借我點錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑和吃飯都是需要錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才特意來讓我看潤的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能保護潤的只有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人我想讓你保護下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啟病毒的患者 已經開始結晶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:36.04,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(867,665)}cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 你去聯繫四分儀等這邊下指令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們接下來要去point yellow one
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你一小時後來接我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有原諒你做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤是無罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著 很快就要用上這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 潤 稍微忍耐一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好遺傳因數捕捉器了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統已經準備好了 為什麼要用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想瞭解熱戀中的物件難道不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安？為什麼會被發現？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明擺著肯定會這樣 現在快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是葬儀社嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是陷阱！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造出一條逃跑的線路 引誘敵人是基本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種外行人的想法會讓你喪命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有虛空 能把人心具象化為武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:44.32,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形兵器也可以打倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.42,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(528,665)}endrave
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我會相信嗎 外面的那些人說不定是你叫來的吧 這偽善者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會像你一樣背叛別人 拋棄別人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會按說好的幫潤逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷尋只要閉上嘴讓我抽就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 你的哥哥沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你嗎 沒臉的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤 我很快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 逃吧逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天可是特別的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙會追那個光的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有一手呢 那麼 連射怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 噓界 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是預想之外但是這也挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個東西 和天啟病毒的結晶化 居然起了同樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:59.88,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(659,665)}cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移了？發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潤！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼向谷尋交代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啟病毒引起了機器裡的基因共鳴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 在那裡的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重啟指令…能輸的全給我輸入進去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了 發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓界少佐 太危險了 請撤離！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且先撤退 作戰中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 六本木？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落的聖誕節之前的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？ 潤？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能說上話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是特別的喲 因為是生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2029年12月24日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最幸福的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 失落的聖誕節就將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅帶著這段幸福的回憶 我已經想離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 請用那虛空切斷我的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:18.75,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(585,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的虛空是切斷生命的虛空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:23.73,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(697,665)}void                      void
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了埋葬我的虛空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:28.16,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(764,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取我自由的結晶 賜予了我能看到虛空的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:44.09,Default-副,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(905,665)}void
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過那雙眼看到的哥哥裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有另一個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃披薩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜歡的有番茄的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥幫你買哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累贅 你是個累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經多次看到了善良的人們當中不善良的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 親戚裡的阿姨 醫療設施的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概集 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這麼活下去的話 這份悲痛肯定會不斷襲擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至會開始討厭哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望活在喜歡著優秀的哥哥的時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快動手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落的聖誕節？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好可怕 好可怕喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 有哥哥在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 這樣下去我會殺掉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我只是個麻煩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把哥哥的人生變得一團糟吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很 討厭我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也對哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生總是事與願違呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 潤…潤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,



